column6: She rubs a brush on her face
She holds up a lighter foundation to the camera
She begins applying foundation to the upper part of both cheeks and under her nose via dots
She rubs in the dots of foundation with a larger round brush and rubs it around her eye
she brushes down with the foundation to even out the foundation
She looks through her makeup kit and checks the foundation applied in the mirror
She brushes setting powder under her eye left to right
She applies primer on her eye lids and rubs it in with the pads of her fingers
She looks to the side to read the chat
she uses a brush to blend in a setting powder
she holds up an setting powder pallet with the skin color powder she is using
she makes small circles with her brush on her eyelids with the light eye shadow
She holds up the palmaid|| an eye brow colorant|| to the camera and then opens the package
She holds up the packaging for the makeup that shows the makeup container is half the size of the packaging
She brushes her eye brows upward
